OL,3,CPhone and broadband providers banned
OL,4,Cfrom linking prices to inflation
OL,6,FRegulator Ofcom has said it will
OL,7,Fprohibit mobile phone carriers and
OL,8,Fbroadband providers from linking
OL,9,Fprices to high inflation figures
OL,10,Fduring a customer's contract.
OL,12,FOn Friday, new rules from the watchdog
OL,13,Fwill require companies to be upfront
OL,14,Fand disclose any price increases.
OL,16,FThis will mean from January next year,
OL,17,Fany price increases in a contract must
OL,18,Fbe stated in pounds and pence.
