OL,3,CPhone and broadband providers banned
OL,4,Cfrom linking prices to inflation
OL,6,FMany major phone, broadband and paid
OL,7,FTV services currently link their price
OL,8,Frises to future inflation rates, which
OL,9,F"unfairly" puts the burden of rising
OL,10,Finflation costs onto customers, Ofcom
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We have decided to ban this
OL,14,Fpractice," it added.
OL,16,FSaying that people "cannot predict"
OL,17,Finflation and "do not understand (it)
OL,18,Fwell".
