OL,3,CPhone and broadband providers banned
OL,4,Cfrom linking prices to inflation
OL,6,FIt is a confirmation of rules that the
OL,7,Fregulator said it was looking at in
OL,8,FDecember 2023.
OL,10,FOfcom telecoms policy director
OL,11,FCristina Luna-Esteban said: "With
OL,12,Fhousehold budgets squeezed, people
OL,13,Fneed to have certainty about their
OL,14,Fmonthly outgoings.
OL,16,F"But that's impossible if you're tied
OL,17,Finto a contract where the price could
OL,18,Fchange based on something as hard to
OL,19,Fpredict as future inflation.
