OL,3,CPhone and broadband providers banned
OL,4,Cfrom linking prices to inflation
OL,6,F"We're stepping in on behalf of phone,
OL,7,Fbroadband and pay TV customers to
OL,8,Fstamp out this practice, so people can
OL,9,Fbe certain of the price they will pay,
OL,10,Fcompare deals more easily and take
OL,11,Fadvantage of the competitive market we
OL,12,Fhave in the UK."
